mobisocial.musubi.ui.util

Class IntentProxyActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • Activity
      • mobisocial.musubi.ui.util.IntentProxyActivity

  • public class IntentProxyActivity
extends Activity
    A utility class that launches a resolved intent for a result and returns back to the caller the component used to carry out the intent.
